      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is in poor condition and is looking for a new owner ready to give it some serious mechanical TLC. While it currently needs significant work to get back on the road, it serves as an affordable and exciting foundation for anyone looking to build their own custom ride or use it for parts!",
