      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously curated and mechanically beyond reproach, this unit represents a premier acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. Available now for the sophisticated collector.",
